                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6393" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1630</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8095 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智慧气象——广西气象科学研究所之蝶变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent meteorology：The transformation process of Guangxi Institute of Meteorological Science</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙庆，王志强，周长辉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广西壮族自治区气象科学研究所</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科研、咨询业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智慧气象；科研院所；转型；服务  </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent meteorology; Research institution,;Transformation,;Service</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公益类科研院所承担着科学研究和服务保障国家战略的双重任务，常常陷入“科研和业务两张皮”的发展困境。本案例以广西气象科学研究所的“蝶变”历程为线索，呈现了其转型的全过程，即从科研与业务相对脱节向二者紧密结合转型，从传统的粗放式气象服务向精密监测、精准预报、精细服务的智慧气象服务转型，履行了社会责任，实现了服务国家和造福人民的目标；重点描述了该所面对转型中的种种障碍，通过需求寻求机会，进行资源整合和协同创新的过程；展示了转型后，社会的质疑、兄弟单位的不满、内部的懈怠以及不尽人意的评估结果给领导者带来的新的挑战和决策难题。本案例适用于组织转型、领导力、组织社会责任等课程的教学中，旨在引导学生了解组织转型的动因及过程，掌握推动组织转型的管理思想与对策，提升解决组织转型中矛盾性目标的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As undertaking the dual tasks of scientific research and service guarantee of national strategy, public research institutes often fall into the dilemma of scientific research and meteorological service division. This case shows the transformation process of Guangxi Institute of Meteorological Science. The process contains two stages: First one is transforming from separation to integration between scientific research and service work. Second one is transforming from providing traditional meteorological service to providing intelligent meteorological service which contains precision monitor, accurate prediction, and fine service. Guangxi Institute of Meteorological Science fulfilled social responsibility and achieved the goal of serving national strategy and people through the transformation. Especially, the case describes how Guangxi Institute of Meteorological Science solved obstacles through seeking opportunities, collaborative innovation, and resource integration. Moreover, the case gives a decision problem for leaders and describes new challenges in future, including doubts from the society, dissatisfaction from partners, low working motivation and unsatisfactory performance. The case can be used in the courses of organizational transformation, leadership, and organizational social responsibility to guide students to understand the motivation and process of organizational transformation, master management strategy, and improve the ability of solving trade-off goals. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织转型》、《领导力》、《组织社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织转型理论；协同创新理论；组织社会责任理论；组织双元能力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
